channel.title: Free e-mail addresses
channel.description:
Free e-mail addresses
I am now offering free e-mail services.
Addresses you can get:
@notna.uk.to @notna.us.to @doognotna.co.nz
More coming soon.
Includes: Up to 2mb per message Unlimited space
Post one that you want, eg "nsdfds@notna.uk.to" in this topic. I will PM you with the password and server information for your mail client.
These will work with MSN.
